Dear <%= @invite.invite_name %>,

Your friend, <%= @invitee %>, has invited you to join the HYPTYO List.

HYPTYO is a site, mailing list and online community keeping you up to
date with Tokyo's most interesting places and events. Each week, our
writers and subscribers cut through the clutter of listings, concert
calendars and hearsay to serve up useful info on the best Tokyo has
to offer.

This is a closed list, and <%= @invitee %> has chosen to give you one of his/ 
her two precious invites. If you join, you'll get two invites as
well, with chances to earn more.

Want to join us? If so, click this link:
http://www.hyptyo.com/invite/activate?activation_code=<%=@invite.activation_code %>


Thanks!

The HYPTYO Team

HYPTYO: Primo Tokyo Info

